{"tid":425614,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"做左3年startup IT, 轉大公司係咪已經不可能","createTime":"2017-10-06T01:05:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-06T03:42:45.000Z","uid":13862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"46493d5fb4e3296e87d7741c7c3daff0ee04cc3e","tid":425614,"uid":13862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T01:05:57.000Z","msg":"一畢業就做左呢份工，一早就做左三年，<br />\n由於startup 人手關係，好多野都一腳踢，<br />\n所以儲左一大堆好多元化而好淺既經驗。<br />\n<br />\nPHP, NodeJS, 砌網，<br />\nios swift, android, 上架，cocos2d, 篤manday, qa,<br />\nproject management, agile, waterflow, <br />\nproduct design, <br />\n<br />\n但時間耐左，想轉下環境，<br />\n當我開jobsdb 睇下有咩工。<br />\n<br />\n好似咩都揀唔到咁，<br />\n大家既job description 都似乎係需要數年既單一經驗，而instead of 乜都識少少。<br />\n<br />\n但又無理由直接跳番落Junior, 好似自己都唔認自己經驗咁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你地會點做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c37beec2271ad6e684f693effa75e7d4ce43cefd","tid":425614,"uid":42799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T03:42:45.000Z","msg":"Full stack developer 好值錢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}